 (šiwāh) is cross-referenced under ش و ه (š w h). Compare Hebrew שֶׂה (śe)."},"ipa":["/ʃaː.ʔa/","/ʃaːʔ/"],"lanes_definition":null,"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%B4%D8%A7%D8%A1/","headword_ar":"شاء","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_48","lexicon_en":"Sultan Qaboos Encyclopedia of Arab Names (Sultan Qaboos University, 1985)","lexicon_ar":"موسوعة السلطان قابوس لأسماء العرب","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=124270#29da11","body_html":"شاء<br>من (ش و ه) الواحدة من الضأن والمعز والظباء والبقر والنعام. يستخدم للإناث."}]}}